<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Gopal Tiwari | DevOps Portfolio</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #050816;
      color: white;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(0,255,255,0.12), transparent 25%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(162,0,255,0.15), transparent 30%);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(5, 8, 22, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      z-index: 999;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 0;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #00d9ff;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 30px;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #00d9ff;
    }

    .btn {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d9ff, #8b5cf6);
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: 0.3s;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,217,255,0.4);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,217,255,0.8);
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      gap: 50px;
      padding: 60px 0;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: 75px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-text h1 span {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #00d9ff, #8b5cf6);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .hero-text p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .glass {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .hero-image {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-image img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 550px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 25px #00d9ff);
    }

    section {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 45px;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .section-title span {
      color: #00d9ff;
    }

    .tech-stack {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .tech-card {
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .tech-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,217,255,0.4);
    }

    .tech-card i {
      font-size: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #00d9ff;
    }

    .pipeline {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .pipeline-step {
      padding: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .pipeline-step:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      border-color: #00d9ff;
    }

    .pipeline-step h3 {
      margin-top: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .projects {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .project-card {
      padding: 30px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .project-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(139,92,246,0.4);
    }

    .project-card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #00d9ff;
    }

    .project-card p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .about {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 50px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,217,255,0.5);
    }

    .about-text h2 {
      font-size: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-text p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .skills {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .skills span {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    @media(max-width: 1000px) {
      .hero,
      .about {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-text h1 {
        font-size: 55px;
      }

      .hero-buttons {
        justify-content: center;
      }

      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .nav-links {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <nav>
        <div class="logo">🚀 DevOps Journey</div>

        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="#pipeline">Pipeline</a></li>
          <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about">About Me</a></li>
        </ul>

        <a href="https://github.com" class="btn">GitHub</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero container" id="home">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>
        FROM CODE TO <br>
        <span>PRODUCTION</span>
      </h1>

      <p>
        DevOps Engineer | CI/CD | Kubernetes | GitOps <br><br>
        Automating deployments with Jenkins, Docker,
        Kubernetes & ArgoCD.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#pipeline" class="btn">Explore Pipeline</a>
        <a href="https://github.com" class="btn">View GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/919/919853.png" alt="DevOps">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span>Tech</span> Stack</h2>

      <div class="tech-stack">
        <div class="tech-card glass">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-jenkins"></i>
          <h3>Jenkins</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-card glass">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-docker"></i>
          <h3>Docker</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-card glass">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i>
          <h3>GitHub</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-card glass">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-dharmachakra"></i>
          <h3>Kubernetes</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-card glass">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-code-branch"></i>
          <h3>ArgoCD</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-card glass">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-aws"></i>
          <h3>AWS</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-card glass">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-linux"></i>
          <h3>Linux</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-card glass">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-git-alt"></i>
          <h3>Git</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="pipeline">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">CI/CD <span>Pipeline</span></h2>

      <div class="pipeline">
        <div class="pipeline-step glass">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-github fa-3x"></i>
          <h3>Checkout Code</h3>
          <p>Pull latest code from GitHub</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pipeline-step glass">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-docker fa-3x"></i>
          <h3>Build Image</h3>
          <p>Create Docker image automatically</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pipeline-step glass">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-upload fa-3x"></i>
          <h3>Push Image</h3>
          <p>Push Docker image to DockerHub</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pipeline-step glass">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-code-merge fa-3x"></i>
          <h3>Update Manifest</h3>
          <p>Update Kubernetes deployment YAML</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pipeline-step glass">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket fa-3x"></i>
          <h3>ArgoCD Sync</h3>
          <p>Deploy application automatically</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="projects">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Featured <span>Projects</span></h2>

      <div class="projects">
        <div class="project-card glass">
          <h3>Jenkins CI/CD Pipeline</h3>
          <p>
            Built automated CI/CD pipeline using Jenkins,
            Docker and Kubernetes with GitHub integration.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card glass">
          <h3>GitOps Deployment with ArgoCD</h3>
          <p>
            Implemented GitOps workflow using ArgoCD
            for automatic Kubernetes synchronization.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card glass">
          <h3>Kubernetes Deployment</h3>
          <p>
            Managed containerized applications using
            Deployments, Services and NodePort.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <div class="container about">
      <div>
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/4140/4140048.png" alt="Profile">
      </div>

      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Hi, I'm <span style="color:#00d9ff">Gopal Tiwari</span></h2>

        <p>
          DevOps Engineer passionate about automation,
          cloud infrastructure and scalable deployments.
          I enjoy working with CI/CD, Kubernetes,
          Docker and GitOps workflows.
        </p>

        <div class="skills">
          <span>Docker</span>
          <span>Kubernetes</span>
          <span>Jenkins</span>
          <span>GitHub</span>
          <span>ArgoCD</span>
          <span>AWS</span>
          <span>Linux</span>
          <span>CI/CD</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 Gopal Tiwari | DevOps Engineer | Building Automation • Deploying Innovation
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
